CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1962, pg. A20 reads: "Salute - Mrs. Elvenia Yarborough (right) is shown presenting flowers to Mrs. W.C. Stallworth, as Mrs. Stallworth and her husband celebrated their 44th wedding anniversary. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. W.C. Stallworth being presented with flowers by Elvenia Yarborough during the Stallworth's forty-fourth wedding anniversary party in YMCA
